This product is a derivative work that ports the following library to TypeScript:

  hwplib (https://github.com/neolord0/hwplib)
  Copyright neolord0
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

The original hwplib bundles portions of Apache POI (POIFS/HPSF) for OLE2 compound
file handling. In this port that layer is instead provided at runtime by:

  js-cfb  (https://github.com/SheetJS/js-cfb)   — Apache-2.0
  fflate  (https://github.com/101arrowz/fflate) — MIT
